message: Media outlets reported on allegations and investigations, but it's crucial to note that these reports rely on individual statements. The US Center for SafeSport hasn't publicly provided suspension details, meaning article info is based on hearsay. Lack of primary source verification raises accuracy concerns. Wikipedia's policy emphasizes well-sourced, unbiased, verifiable info, especially in sensitive cases. The hearsay-based content of this section doesn't meet reliable sourcing guidelines.
